textfsm_template:
Value HA_STATE (Active|Standby)
Value HA_STATUS (Ready|Not Ready)
Value LOCAL_HA_ID (\d+)
Value PEER_HA_ID (\d+)
Value CLUSTER_HA_MODE (Active-Passive|Active-Active)
Value LAST_HEARTBEAT (.+)
Value FAILOVER_COUNT (\d+)
Value ACTIVE_UPTIME (\d+ days, \d+ hours, \d+ minutes)

Start
  ^HA State: ${HA_STATE}\s*$$
  ^Overall HA Status: ${HA_STATUS}\s*$$
  ^Local HA ID: ${LOCAL_HA_ID}\s*$$
  ^Peer HA ID: ${PEER_HA_ID}\s*$$
  ^Cluster HA Mode: ${CLUSTER_HA_MODE}\s*$$
  ^Last Heartbeat: ${LAST_HEARTBEAT}$$
  ^Failover Count: ${FAILOVER_COUNT}\s*$$
  ^Active Uptime: ${ACTIVE_UPTIME}\s*$$ -> Record
